---
layout: layout.njk
title: "Paul Pincente"
---

<section id="about" class="window">
  <div class="titlebar">
    <span class="led"></span>
    <span class="title">MY STORY</span>
    <div class="window-controls">
      <button class="btn-close" aria-label="Close">✖</button>
      <button class="btn-min" aria-label="Minimize">—</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="window-content">
    <p>
      Hi, I’m Paul. My first computer was a VIC-20, and I’ve been obsessed with tech ever since.
      That spark turned into building staking infrastructure for millions of dollars in assets — 
      and now I’m exploring the future of blockchain, AI, and digital wealth.
    </p>
    <p>
      I love pushing limits, blending nostalgia with cutting-edge innovation, and telling stories through code.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="skills" class="window">
  <div class="titlebar">
    <span class="led"></span>
    <span class="title">WHAT I PLAY WITH</span>
    <div class="window-controls">
      <button class="btn-close" aria-label="Close">✖</button>
      <button class="btn-min" aria-label="Minimize">—</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="window-content">
    <p>Things I like to tinker with:</p>
    <ul>
      {% for skill in skills %}
        <li>{{ skill }}</li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    <p>And yes, the occasional retro game emulator.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="experience" class="window">
  <div class="titlebar">
    <span class="led"></span>
    <span class="title">PAST ADVENTURES</span>
    <div class="window-controls">
      <button class="btn-close" aria-label="Close">✖</button>
      <button class="btn-min" aria-label="Minimize">—</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="window-content">
    {% for job in experience %}
      <div class="job">
        <h3>{{ job.title }} @ {{ job.company }}</h3>
        <p><strong>{{ job.dates }}</strong></p>
        <p>
          {% if job.title == "Vice President, Digital Assets Products" %}
            At Purpose Investments, I didn’t just launch ETFs — I helped bring traditional finance into the blockchain era.
          {% elif job.title == "Blockchain Infrastructure & Analytics Architect" %}
            At Ether Capital, I built top-performing Ethereum validators and developed a staking analytics platform that empowered business decisions.
          {% elif job.title == "Co-Founder / CEO" %}
            Starting Growratio was a journey of innovation, creating IoT platforms and patented products in partnership with Microsoft.
          {% else %}
            {{ job.highlights | join(', ') }}
          {% endif %}
        </p>
      </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

<section id="resume" class="window">
  <div class="titlebar">
    <span class="led"></span>
    <span class="title">RESUME</span>
    <div class="window-controls">
      <button class="btn-close" aria-label="Close">✖</button>
      <button class="btn-min" aria-label="Minimize">—</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="window-content">
    <iframe src="/assets/resume.pdf" width="100%" height="600" title="Resume PDF"></iframe>
    <a href="/assets/resume.pdf" download>Download Resume</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="window">
  <div class="titlebar">
    <span class="led"></span>
    <span class="title">LET'S CONNECT</span>
    <div class="window-controls">
      <button class="btn-close" aria-label="Close">✖</button>
      <button class="btn-min" aria-label="Minimize">—</button>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="window-content">
    <p>Want to talk crypto, AI, or retro games? Drop me a line:</p>
    <p>Email: <a href="mailto:{{ author.email }}">{{ author.email }}</a></p>
    <p>LinkedIn: <a href="{{ author.linkedin }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ author.linkedin }}</a></p>
  </div>
</section>
